    <item>
      <title>意大利将把安赛乐米塔尔旗下的钢铁制造商国有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/italy-is-set-to-nationalize-steelmaker-owned-by-arcelormittal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谈判失败后，总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 领导的政府准备从主要股东安赛乐米塔尔公司 (ArcelorMittal SA) 手中夺取该国最大钢铁制造商的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/italy-is-set-to-nationalize-steelmaker-owned-by-arcelormittal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 16:22:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党誓言与寻求英国上市的科技公司合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/davos-2024-britain-should-be-proud-of-banking-sector-says-labour-s-reynolds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党商业发言人表示，工党政府将与希望在伦敦上市的科技公司合作，因为英国主要反对党试图在预计将于秋季举行的选举之前提升其商业信誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/davos-2024-britain-should-be-proud-of-banking-sector-says-labour-s-reynolds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 16:20:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>林德纳表示德国过多的公共支出将损害欧洲央行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/davos-2024-lindner-says-too-much-german-public-spending-would-undermine-ecb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 表示，德国不能继续大规模公共支出，因为这将破坏欧洲央行抑制通胀的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/davos-2024-lindner-says-too-much-german-public-spending-would-undermine-ecb</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 16:07:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦和伊朗为何互相攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/pakistan-iran-tensions-why-they-have-attacked-each-other</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦和伊朗之间的关系总体上是友好的，尽管两国在900公里长（560英里长）的边界沿线遭受武装分子袭击的问题上时断时续地发生争执。随着两个穆斯林国家在彼此领土上发动袭击，紧张局势再次加剧。来自伊朗的第一次袭击发生在伊朗向其所谓的以色列在伊拉克间谍基地和伊斯兰国在叙利亚的目标发射导弹后不久。伊朗战争结束后的一次引人注目的武力展示]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/pakistan-iran-tensions-why-they-have-attacked-each-other</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 15:38:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登的新学生债务计划面临民权和劳工组织的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/student-loan-forgiveness-civil-rights-labor-groups-press-biden-on-relief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统面临着近 70 个倡导团体的压力，要求扩大政府即将发布的替代债务减免计划的范围，这些团体表示，这些改变对于帮助对他的连任竞选至关重要的群体（包括年轻人和有色人种）是必要的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/student-loan-forgiveness-civil-rights-labor-groups-press-biden-on-relief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对也门的空袭使红海南部航运业陷入新的混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/red-sea-attacks-strikes-and-houthis-ensure-shipping-chaos-on-vital-routes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在红海商船遭受数周袭击后，美国和英国决定对胡塞武装分子进行反击，这只会加剧整个航运业的混乱，突显出船舶在这条重要贸易航线上航行时所面临的持久供应链危机的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/red-sea-attacks-strikes-and-houthis-ensure-shipping-chaos-on-vital-routes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 13:52:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普采取行动粉碎国会对乌克兰和边境协议的希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/trump-moves-to-quash-hopes-of-ukraine-border-deal-in-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统、可能的共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普正在采取行动，粉碎两党在移民和乌克兰问题上达成妥协的希望，因为参议院最早将于下周就一项可能的协议进行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/trump-moves-to-quash-hopes-of-ukraine-border-deal-in-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 12:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
